<blockquote>
<p>MEMORANDUM TO SITE DIRECTOR STONE</p>
<p>We currently believe that the research object has been written about in the scripture for various religious groups dealing with paranormal activity.</p>
<p>They refer to it unanimously in terminology that describe it as &quot;empty&quot; and at other times like a portal to their underworlds, or similar theological concepts. Descriptions generally refer to it as all black, and hostile.</p>
<p>The similarities to the research objects are obvious. As such, we should take precaution against any word of this entity being held, as it may incur an attack by these organizations.</p>
<p>Therefore, we recommend that the current in-construction Site-12 be selected as the location for the entity, due to its remote location and high security.</p>
<p>Colonel Ritts</p>
<p>American Secure Containment Initiative</p>
</blockquote>
